pageContext.claim: “Well, it would seem like [Beirut was an attack], based on the explosion. I've met with some of our great generals, and they just seem to feel that it was. This was not a -- some kind of a manufacturing explosion type of event. This was a -- seems to be, according to them -- they would know better than I would, but they seem to think it was a attack.”
pageContext.analysis: The explosion in Beirut was not an attack.
